1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,237
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:52,912 --> 00:00:54,821
(Huaying Pharma)
They've formed an investigation team.

4
00:00:55,090 --> 00:00:56,000
We'll fully cooperate.

5
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,780
All drugs from the same batch
have already been recalled.

6
00:00:57,799 --> 00:01:00,520
We've contacted everyone involved
and are negotiating compensation.

7
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:01,159
Good.

8
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:03,039
Meet all their demands

9
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:04,359
no matter what they ask for.

10
00:01:04,662 --> 00:01:05,012
Okay.

11
00:01:06,090 --> 00:01:07,950
What about the results
of our internal tests?

12
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:09,840
The routine test reports are ready.

13
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,040
All indicators are normal.

14
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,159
Keep following up.

15
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:12,599
Understood

16
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:13,520
And you.

17
00:01:13,530 --> 00:01:14,990
I told you to control
the public opinion.

18
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:15,840
What happened?

19
00:01:16,050 --> 00:01:18,270
Why is the whole city
still blasting us with criticism?

20
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,200
I can't control it, Mr. Qin.

21
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:19,959
Lives are involved.

22
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:20,799
It's too sensitive.

23
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,600
I don't care what you do.

24
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:23,999
Suppress this matter now!

25
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:24,599
Got it?

26
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,480
Yes.

27
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:26,560
Everyone,

28
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:29,120
this concerns the survival
of Huaying Pharma.

29
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:32,000
I expect you to give all your effort.

30
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:32,920
Understood?

31
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,840
- Yes!
- Yes!

32
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,799
Worried, huh?

33
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,799
Why are you here?

34
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,300
With something so big,
of course I'd come to watch the show.

35
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,599
Ye Chen,

36
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,799
I'm busy right now.

37
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,510
I don't have time for your nonsense.

38
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:08,259
Tell me.

39
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:09,879
How can I help?

40
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,199
You? Help me?

41
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:17,150
Although this mess

42
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:18,425
has nothing to do with me,

43
00:02:18,875 --> 00:02:20,560
I'm Aoxue's master after all.

44
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,199
Besides,

45
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:25,240
the Ninefold True Essence Pill
belongs to our ancestors.

46
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,199
If it gets ruined just like this,

47
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,560
it'll be a huge loss
for Huaxia's medical scene.

48
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,400
Thank you for the offer.

49
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,360
Although

50
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,840
you are Aoxue's master,

51
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:39,240
you're not a Qin.

52
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:42,080
So you don't need to worry about this.

53
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,000
So you still don't trust me after all.

54
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,319
Old man,

55
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,719
didn't you say you wanted to bet on me?

56
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:48,759
What?

57
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:51,300
You're backing out
before the cards are revealed?

58
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,319
You want to gamble?

59
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:56,919
Sure.

60
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,879
I'll take the bet with you.

61
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,000
I'd like to see what kind of card

62
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,400
you're holding.

63
00:03:04,612 --> 00:03:06,125
Now that's more like it.

64
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,039
The Ninefold True Essence Pill
was developed

65
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,840
based on an ancient formula left

66
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:21,200
by a folk miracle doctor.

67
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:23,000
It contains nine ingredients

68
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:25,990
and prepared with an ancient method
of nine rounds of steaming and drying.

69
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:28,120
These are the raw material samples.

70
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:31,680
The company

71
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,280
invested a great deal

72
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:35,680
to develop this medicine.

73
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:37,738
(Product Inspection Report)
I had very high expectations for it.

74
00:03:37,950 --> 00:03:40,432
I hoped it would become
the company's flagship.

75
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,702
So our quality control
was extremely strict.

76
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:46,080
We checked from source itself.

77
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:47,680
This time

78
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:49,000
we conducted routine checks

79
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,560
after the incident occurred,

80
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:51,639
but found no nothing.

81
00:03:51,925 --> 00:03:53,520
A more detailed testing

82
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,560
will take some time.

83
00:03:58,610 --> 00:04:00,890
What symptoms did the people
with adverse reactions show?

84
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,000
Allergic reactions.

85
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,159
Dizziness.

86
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:04,439
Vomiting.

87
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,800
Ascites.

88
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,759
And jaundice.

89
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,048
The most severe ones had liver failure.

90
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,199
How did you know?

91
00:04:10,530 --> 00:04:12,639
Someone mixed fake notoginseng
into the notoginseng.

92
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,599
Not only

93
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,879
do these two have similar names,

94
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,590
but their appearance is also very alike.

95
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:21,170
Once dried, both look
like grayish-yellow root lumps.

96
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:22,970
The slice patterns are also similar.

97
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,120
Anyone without deep expertise

98
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,959
can't tell them apart.

99
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:28,920
They both also

100
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,360
contrain notoginsenoside R1.

101
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:31,800
Routine checks

102
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,279
won't detect the difference.

103
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:35,225
Fake notoginseng has no medical effect.

104
00:04:35,490 --> 00:04:37,000
Instead, it has pyrrolidine alkaloid.

105
00:04:37,210 --> 00:04:39,439
That causes those adverse reactions
you just mentioned.

106
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,839
Anyone who did this

107
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:45,040
must know the production process
of Ninefold True Essence Pill very well.

108
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,925
It has to be an insider.

109
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:55,700
Anyone came today?

110
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,560
Liu Baoliang from production.

111
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:58,560
Where is he?

112
00:04:59,040 --> 00:04:59,759
He left.

113
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,900
It's been more than an hour.

114
00:05:03,650 --> 00:05:04,279
Call the police.

115
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:06,800
Thank you, officer.

116
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,160
Goodbye.

117
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,600
It's over.

118
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,000
He's run away.

119
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:13,279
What about this?

120
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,720
I'll arrange for someone

121
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:17,040
to release a notice
explaining the situation.

122
00:05:17,050 --> 00:05:18,190
We'll calm the public first.

123
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,000
If you release a statement now,

124
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:23,490
not only will it fail to calm the public
but it'll also add fuel to the fire.

125
00:05:23,770 --> 00:05:25,115
Your surveillance footage is gone.

126
00:05:25,237 --> 00:05:26,258
Your witness has fled.

127
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,360
You have no proof.

128
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,839
How will the public believe you?

129
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,759
They'll say you're dodging
the real issue

130
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:32,830
and avoiding responsibility.

131
00:05:32,850 --> 00:05:33,600
Believe it or not,

132
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,519
the keyboard warriors will slander you
for silencing witnesses.

133
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,639
How was that man when he worked for you?

134
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,720
He's been with me for nearly ten years.

135
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,879
He was always honest and reliable.

136
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,040
That's why

137
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,360
I promoted him.

138
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,120
And I paid him well.

139
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,759
For him to betray you suddenly,

140
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:55,720
either he was threatened,

141
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:58,279
or someone offered him

142
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:00,160
something he couldn't reuse.

143
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,120
You're saying someone
used him against me?

144
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:08,399
I'm afraid this plan
started a long time ago.

145
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:13,680
Hello.

146
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,600
Hi, Mr. Qin.

147
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,460
What is it?

148
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,600
Ohara Pharma just released a statement

149
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:19,079
saying Ninefold True Essence Pill

150
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,680
stole the formula for their Shinbu Pill.

151
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,319
You really called it.

152
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,560
Ohara Pharma released a statement

153
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,120
claiming that we

154
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,720
stole their Shinbu Pill formula.

155
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,600
But because our process was wrong

156
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,862
that caused these issues.

157
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,759
They're officially suing us now.

158
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,040
Ohara Pharma?

159
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:41,480
Our old rival.

160
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:43,879
It seems

161
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:46,000
they're kicking us while we're down.

162
00:06:48,375 --> 00:06:50,160
I think it's more than that.

163
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,920
They want to kick you down the cliff
and then stone you to death.

164
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,439
The name sounds
like a Japanese pharma company.

165
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,600
Yes.

166
00:06:58,199 --> 00:07:00,439
This is their person in charge
for Huaxia,

167
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,000
Ichiro Ohara.

168
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,680
He was also
at the Song family's banquet.

169
00:07:07,475 --> 00:07:08,639
Tang Sihai.

170
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,920
Who gave you this?

171
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,960
What were you talking
about with Ichiro Ohara?

172
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,720
Just casual conversation.

173
00:07:16,010 --> 00:07:17,700
Talking about how
to harm Qin Gang, right?

174
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,600
Do you know who he is?

175
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,639
A businessman.

176
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:21,680
He's Japanese.

177
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,350
He's still a businessman
no matter where he's from.

178
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,862
What he's doing isn't business!

179
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,040
Ye Chen,

180
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:29,399
you won't believe me
no matter what I say, huh?

181
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,720
(Sued by Ohara Pharma)
Baoyuan Hall,

182
00:07:37,050 --> 00:07:37,879
(Yixin Pharma patent infringement)
Yixin Pharma,

183
00:07:38,037 --> 00:07:39,040
and Changsheng Pharma.

184
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:41,040
They're all the same as the Qin family.

185
00:07:41,639 --> 00:07:44,079
Their products first
got exposed for quality issues.

186
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,839
Than Ohara Pharma sued them

187
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:47,250
claiming they stole patents!

188
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,240
They lost in the end.

189
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,600
They're a group of vicious capitalists
targeting domestic

190
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,800
pharmaceutical companies!

191
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,600
The weak get beaten.

192
00:07:56,425 --> 00:07:58,278
If you can't fight back, you die.

193
00:07:58,987 --> 00:08:00,929
That's just how the world works.

194
00:08:01,650 --> 00:08:03,680
They attack local pharma companies.

195
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,879
They're humiliating our medicine.

196
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,360
You are heir to the Ye family.

197
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,040
They can't touch you.

198
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,560
I am heir to the Ye family,

199
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:13,639
but I'm also Chinese.

200
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,279
Don't tell me

201
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,040
you're doing this

202
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,360
for national medicine

203
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,959
or some grand national cause.

204
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:25,680
Can we not throw these big words around?

205
00:08:28,262 --> 00:08:29,382
I'm doing this for myself.

206
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:33,689
So that I won't become someone like you.

207
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:49,960
So?

208
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:51,639
You're helping me

209
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,200
or Wang Dongxue?

210
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,480
Friendship is precious,

211
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,690
but love is more important.

212
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,000
You jerk!

213
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,279
I wasn't finished.

214
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,600
If it's for money,

215
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,639
both can be abandoned.

216
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,120
Listen.

217
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,480
If you can settle this matter for me,

218
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:15,080
you'll be Huaying Pharma's savior.

219
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:18,639
You know how Qin Gang is.

220
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:22,080
He won't mind
about giving you a little reward.

221
00:09:24,825 --> 00:09:25,320
Alright.

222
00:09:25,330 --> 00:09:26,300
What do you need me for?

223
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,440
Investigate him.

224
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:30,440
Liu Baoliang.

225
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,879
Huaying Pharma's production manager.

226
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:36,000
(Employee Records: Liu Baoliang)
Suspected for swapping the ingredient.

227
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:37,879
Don't worry.

228
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,120
Leave it to me.

229
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:42,519
That's more like it.

230
00:09:50,625 --> 00:09:52,712
(Control Room)

231
00:10:01,162 --> 00:10:02,460
(Huaying Pharma Employee Records)

232
00:10:15,087 --> 00:10:16,517
- Chen.
- Yeah.

233
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,950
Liu Baoliang looks pretty clean.

234
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,320
No drugs or gambling addiction.

235
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,399
No online loans too.

236
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,039
(Liu Baoliang)
No unusual bank activity too.

237
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,879
I know all these.

238
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:27,840
Good.

239
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,600
I'll tell you something you don't.

240
00:10:31,950 --> 00:10:33,795
(Liu Chengren)
He also has a love child

241
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:36,159
who studied in Japan

242
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:37,679
and interned at Ohara Pharma

243
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,787
for six months.

244
00:10:41,087 --> 00:10:42,410
This Liu Chengren guy

245
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:43,975
also has a cryptocurrency account.

246
00:10:44,587 --> 00:10:46,600
Not long ago, he received a transfer.

247
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:49,240
Based on the exchange,

248
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,679
guess how much he got?

249
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,480
50 million!

250
00:10:56,487 --> 00:10:58,759
As expected of the power
of filthy money.

251
00:10:58,812 --> 00:11:00,600
After Liu Baoliang fled,

252
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:02,120
Liu Chengren disappeared too.

253
00:11:02,210 --> 00:11:03,559
Ran off with the money, I suppose.

254
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,279
Some time ago,

255
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,320
a phone number

256
00:11:06,812 --> 00:11:08,737
(Liu Baoliang, Liu Chengren)
has been contacting them frequently.

257
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,519
The last call

258
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:13,159
was at 2:07 p.m. last Friday

259
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:15,200
(Liu Baoliang)
to Liu Baoliang.

260
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:16,679
2:07 p.m.?

261
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,159
Isn't that exactly when I went
to the Huaying factory?

262
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,287
Who owns the number?

263
00:11:21,762 --> 00:11:23,012
(Xu Lili)

264
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:24,159
Xu Lili.

265
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:27,919
Xu Lili?

266
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,799
I don't remember her.

267
00:11:30,399 --> 00:11:31,559
You don't know her,

268
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,039
but you'll surely know

269
00:11:33,519 --> 00:11:34,559
her ex-boyfriend.

270
00:11:38,087 --> 00:11:39,862
(Qin Aodong)

271
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,200
We barely left,

272
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,279
and Liu Baoliang ran off with the USB.

273
00:11:43,879 --> 00:11:45,600
It was Qin Aodong who tipped him off.

274
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:48,879
That's not possible.

275
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:53,200
He may be a bit foolish,

276
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:55,279
but he wouldn't go this far.

277
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:56,559
Besides,

278
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,480
if Huaying collapses,

279
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,200
what good would it do him?

280
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:03,080
You'll have to ask him yourself.

281
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:04,600
Master,

282
00:12:04,799 --> 00:12:05,919
could there be a mistake?

283
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,639
Even if it's the same number.

284
00:12:07,639 --> 00:12:09,639
It doesn't mean my brother is using it.

285
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,279
Where is he now?

286
00:12:12,562 --> 00:12:15,250
I asked him to keep watch
in the control room.

287
00:12:16,190 --> 00:12:17,039
Connect the cameras.

288
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,120
It's quite easy.

289
00:12:34,570 --> 00:12:35,519
You guys can't do this?

290
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,725
Use a virtual number and call his phone.

291
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:43,559
Stay quiet.

292
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:50,559
Hello?

293
00:12:53,637 --> 00:12:54,559
He's got wit

294
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:55,799
but not much.

295
00:12:58,399 --> 00:12:59,360
Ingrate.

296
00:13:01,039 --> 00:13:02,320
What an ingrate.

297
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,159
How could he do something like this?

298
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,690
With his brains, he shouldn't be able
to do something this big.

299
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:12,879
Ohara Pharma should be behind him.

300
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:15,919
Master,

301
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,000
Aodong might have just made a mistake.

302
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,440
Someone must've used him.

303
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,960
He wouldn't do anything
to hurt the family.

304
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,120
Old man, what do you think?

305
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:29,000
Dong

306
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:30,639
isn't a bad kid.

307
00:13:33,039 --> 00:13:33,720
Can you

308
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:36,679
give him another chance?

309
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:37,879
Sure.

310
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,919
We'll give him one more chance.

311
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,970
Let's hope he's still worth saving.

312
00:14:06,250 --> 00:14:08,738
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

313
00:14:08,825 --> 00:14:12,578
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

314
00:14:13,038 --> 00:14:17,975
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

315
00:14:18,138 --> 00:14:20,425
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

316
00:14:20,738 --> 00:14:23,418
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

317
00:14:24,488 --> 00:14:27,113
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

318
00:14:27,413 --> 00:14:30,425
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

319
00:14:30,625 --> 00:14:33,675
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

320
00:14:33,788 --> 00:14:36,750
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

321
00:14:37,018 --> 00:14:40,175
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

322
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:44,150
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

323
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:47,013
♪I belong to no one♪

324
00:14:47,075 --> 00:14:50,525
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

325
00:14:50,525 --> 00:14:53,200
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

326
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:59,538
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
